@startuml
!theme plain
title v4 CXL Memory Pool Governance for UA-Link Pods
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam roundcorner 12
skinparam defaultFontName DejaVu Sans
left to right direction

component "CXL Fabric / Pool Manager" as FM #D6EAF8
component "CXL Type-3 / Pool Devices" as DEV #FCF3CF
component "Coherence-CE Placement Policy" as CE #D5F5E3
component "Scheduler Admission" as S #E8DAEF
component "OpenZFS Durable Tier" as Z #FADBD8

FM --> DEV : ownership epoch\nlink + RAS + thermal
DEV --> CE : capacity + latency + bandwidth
CE --> S : pool pressure + class suitability
S --> CE : admit / demote / drain
CE --> Z : durable classes via write policy

note bottom of DEV
Volatile CXL cannot acknowledge durability.
Persistent/block roles require ADR-015 media qualification.
end note
@enduml
